buckman sure is lucky to have a neighbor like them! 🐇 

@luckyneighborpdx is nestled in what was originally viking bakery during the early 1900s ⭐️ all the original charm remains! exposed brick! beautiful floors! the feeling that this place has been part of the fabric of the neighborhood for a very long time! it’s fabulous ✨ 

lucky neighbor was built on the belief that the term ‘community’ can actually be pretty exclusionary. rather, the term ‘neighbor’ fosters empathy and curiosity towards those living around you 🏡 

@luckyneighborpdx is sure to become your one stop shop for all things intentional, local, and charming. you can grab a few goodies for a friends birthday, or treat yourself to a one of a kind rug, or cozy wool sweater 🛍️

the space is brimming with inspiration and wonder, so please do yourself a favor and bunny hop over to check it out 🐰

